	dprr:hasNoteText "See MRR 2.465. See Cicero (Fam. 8.8.1) on his conviction for calumnia in a case against M. Tuccius. See also Shackleton Bailey CLF 1.397-398, and CLA 3.192; Weinrib, Phoenix 25, 1971, 149, note 6.\n" .
